dct_title_s: A topographical map of the peninsula of Cape May with the country westward to Maurice River : from original surveys and levelings, excepting the shore-lines of bays and beaches from Cape May Court House southward which are from the plane-table sheets of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey : based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Depths shown by soundings and isolines. "Atlas sheet No. 17 (Cape May)."
dct_publisher_sm: [Trenton, N.J.] : The Survey, 1895 ([N.Y.] : Julius Bien & Co. Lith.)
